snippet.title: hyper videos
snippet.description:
Want to learn about Javascript? This channel covers Javascript topics with videos coming out weekly. These videos range from short topics to immersive workshops. You can learn about:
* Svelte
* Deno
* FunctionalJS
* hyper63
* APIs
and more.
